{"tid":347991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共就算開完19大都唔敢打仗","createTime":"2017-08-05T09:56:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T11:17:07.000Z","uid":3117,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"17a16d3d5e6e7b1921543107418fd2f3c1bdd27b","tid":347991,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:56:10.000Z","msg":"無論印度做d咩 中共都唔會敢打 未開19大就講要平 <br />\n<br />\n穩過渡，開完19大雜種就驚之前清算既殘餘勢力作<br />\n<br />\n亂反佢 而最有可能打仗既時間段應該就係2020年<br />\n<br />\n前後，中共第三架航母建成 台灣又要選總統，個陣<br />\n<br />\n雜種又要為自己永遠做皇帝補路，係最有可能打仗<br />\n<br />\n既時候<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以未來呢幾年香港人都仲要繼續食屎"},{"pid":"a1cad36c11a196e30a95cf41ad3ce7e7aee28054","tid":347991,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T10:04:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c21f2b378ca1039e921f7fd11c812a6c7f2933a0","tid":347991,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T04:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8959e297040aac6b81e567eebc63e29f54ce1b7e","tid":347991,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T12:56:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aacaae8433c82618ee7a1776c333d6cde49a695","tid":347991,"uid":99225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T13:43:31.000Z","msg":"香港都冇咩時候唔係食緊支那啲屎"},{"pid":"048dfccd5759af515ace0262f6f7e7a92512a0f3","tid":347991,"uid":81197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T14:01:35.000Z","msg":"中共唔會打架啦<br />\n一打仗其他地區又暴亂<br />\n美國搵到藉口開你波 <br />\n慢慢燒軍費 <br />\n分分鐘有錢佬走埋 人仔跌<br />\n到時錢又冇 仗又打唔贏<br />\n美國就撚狗咁撚返幾廿年<br />\n資助下地區獨立 <br />\n中國正式解體"},{"pid":"3528274379c06755b616633ad9807122a11f39b7","tid":347991,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T14:35:58.000Z","msg":"根本中共一日執政, 都唔會打仗<br />\n<br />\n因為中共官員和將領 習慣 送自